Class 185 Now In Train Simulator!
On the 3rd of October 2021, Alan Thomson Simulation released the Class 185 DMU Pack, in collaboration with Imbue Studios... click this article to read more!
  Train Simulator   Oct 3, 2021   0   15  Add to Reading List
In collaboration with Imbue Studios, Alan Thomson Simulation (ATS) have worked together to bring us Train Sim players a much anticipated train, the class 185!
The pack features many things, from special liveries across the Class 185's time, to passenger views, to a operational guard panel, and even different cabs!

The train is priced at £19.99 to ATS Subscribers, or for £24.99 to non-subscribers. The train is action packed with 3 different cab's, 2 different interiors for passenger views, 13 liveries for the train across its FTPE and current TPE era's. These are only a few features....
To find out more you can go to the ATS Site and read the manual available on the following page - Alan Thomson Simulation and Imbue Studios – Class 185 Multiple Unit Pack – Alan Thomson Simulation
Or, to see if you want to look into the pack, you can watch this video released by Alan himself on his YouTube channel - (9) Train Simulator 2022: ATS & Imbue Class 185 Showcase - YouTube
Thank you for taking the time to read this post by Taylor (Content Writer for TrainSimDepot) and on behalf of the team, we hope you have a good day!
